trans-unit.source: Defines the interface that associates a duplex channel with a session.
trans-unit.target: Define a interface que associa um canal dúplex a uma sessão.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.IDuplexSessionChannel> interface indicates that an <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.IDuplexChannel> implements <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.IDuplexSession> semantics.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.IDuplexSessionChannel> interface indica que um <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.IDuplexChannel> implementa <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.IDuplexSession> semântica.

trans-unit.source: Given an <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.IDuplexSessionChannel>, its associated <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.IDuplexSession> can be retrieved through the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ISessionChannel%601.Session%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Dado um <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.IDuplexSessionChannel>, seus associados <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.IDuplexSession> podem ser recuperados por meio de <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ISessionChannel%601.Session%2A> propriedade.
